item.title: FRACTAL LOTUS 1
item.description: FRACTAL LOTUS 1 is a complete cryptoart experience featuring the beauty of a lotus flower combined with the infinite worlds of artificial intelligence. About FRACTAL LOTUS 1 The artwork owner receives a Kusama RMRK token, with links to the original PNG art on IPFS.
